99144,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:27:10.000Z","msg":"唔新鮮就會臭"},{"pid":"9125eddaeec91616f4a3ef335410ca1a2533beee","tid":399144,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>希靈魚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登竟然有同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3facca3cf7ec13b3b86f83535b4a4a055d6dd1","tid":399144,"uid":2336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:34:56.000Z","msg":"希靈魚 = 醃過既春"},{"pid":"a72a412ecd5c011cfbd38a35098f91dd8e40f6c5","tid":399144,"uid":83300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:58:08.000Z","msg":"希靈魚白色嘅肉同埋黃色嘅魚籽，係無關係架。希靈魚係希靈魚肉放上醃製過嘅魚籽上壓實。"},{"pid":"2a542b36035c2c2a5f00749993f1997636e64eb2","tid":399144,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:18:18.000Z","msg":"[希靈魚身世之謎!]<br />\n<br />\n希靈魚，往往都係連住黃金色嘅魚籽，有客人曾經問過，點解希靈魚咁奇怪，會有咁多魚籽，有時候，係市面更加見到魚籽多過肉嘅情況!好!就得渡邊SAN解開呢個希靈魚多卵之謎啦!!<br />\n<br />\n其實&hellip;我哋平時見到嘅希靈魚白色嘅肉同埋黃色嘅魚籽，係無關係架!!! 希靈魚肉放上醃製過嘅魚籽上壓實即完成!!<br />\n<br />\n日本人係新年同喜慶都會食希靈魚，喻意像這片魚籽航子孫繁榮，醃製過嘅魚籽低層, 微酸帶香, 口感爽脆有點似蟹子,作為頭盤,絕對開胃一流!<br />\n<br />\n新正頭，緊係要食返啲好意頭食品啦!!今日就嚟渡辺屋買返個[金玉滿堂]餐，同屋企人一齊分享，內有希靈魚壽司，意頭十足，幸福滿載!!!"},{"pid":"548eb41f675791d0fcee5591acae8c73bc654095","tid":399144,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"熊咩屌你"},{"pid":"9744ccc5d82a7ad5685624fb00e50ae5d3aedfc7","tid":399144,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:56:25.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌"},{"pid":"9c98d2b6a64cb1aa1bd6b84d9c02c0377b26ea47","tid":399144,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-